The class updates vim plugins from git. It is useful with vim pathogen extension.

Usage:

create a default config file and add a plugin repo:

updater.php add <plugin-name> <git url>


Remove a repo from config:

updater.php remove <plugin-name> 


List the available repos:

updater.php listconfig


Get the plugin first:

update.php get <plugin-name>


Get all plugin with to the default pathogen folder:(.vim/bundle)

update.php getall


Update only one repos:

update.php update <plugin-name>


Update all plugin repos:

update.php updateall


